item.title: Slow Business
item.description: Not much customer, business is slow so I figured I'd close the store to take a nap or do whatever. That's when my cousin came in asking me if I can keep an eye on his little girl, Sophie. Who am I to say no?

item.title: The Incident At Cherry Lake, Part 4
item.description: As this incident spins out of control everyone begins having emotional reactions beyond anything they had expected, including Derick, and it becomes unclear where this is going.
